root: ^Today was supposed to be an exciting day as it’s the first day of my high school life.
^But my mind is still stuck looking for answers.
^This huge crowd of students doesn’t seem to bother me at all right now even though normally I avoid such places.
^But since I am late today, and I need my thoughts to deviate from that ridiculous dream
^I should push my way through the crowd to find my name in the classlist
